    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>+ In nomine domini dei eterni anno ab incarnatione eius millesimo octogesimo
                        nono mense decembris die septimo. Dum dominus <persName key="#Princeps"
                            ref="#people/3002">iordanis</persName> capuanus <rs key="#Princeps"
                            >princeps</rs> residebat in <rs
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Mention #Function #Residential #Palatium"
                            >palatio</rs> sue <placeName key="#Cities" ref="#places/173"
                            >capue</placeName> ad placitum et iudicium retinendum cum multis <rs
                            key="#Judge">iudicibus</rs> et maxima parte suorum <rs key="#fidelisOf"
                            >fidelium</rs>. inter cetera iudicia fuit litigium inter domnum
                            <persName ref="#people/5048">raulem de azia</persName>. et
                                <persName><name ref="Gherardus Ravenensis">gerardum
                                ravenensem</name></persName>; et <persName><name
                                ref="Gherardus Desonnino">gerardum desonnino</name></persName> et
                        incidens quaestio fuit de pertinentia hereditatis <rs key="#Monasteries"
                            >monasterii</rs>
                        <orgName key="#Monasteries" ref="#juridical_persons/3807">beati stephani de
                            fossanova</orgName>. Quidam videlicet <rs key="#Monks">monachus</rs> in
                        medio deferebat quoddam preceptum eiusdem eacclesiae per quo significabantur
                        omnes <rs key="#Fines">fines</rs> et termini ex omni parte hereditatis
                        predicti monasterii. Et post multas et varias lites, iam dictus princeps
                        precepit iudicibus secundum quod iustitiae ratio eis accommodaret sine
                        dilatione iudicare. Unde <persName key="#Writer #Judge" ref="#people/5049"
                            >rembladus</persName> et <persName key="#Judge" ref="#people/5050"
                            >benedictus</persName>. et <persName key="#Judge" ref="#people/5051"
                            >gregorius</persName>
                        <placeName ref="#places/434" key="#Villages/settlements"
                            >anagnini</placeName>
                        <rs key="#Judge">iudices</rs>. et <persName key="#Judge" ref="#people/5052"
                            >mirando</persName> capuanus <rs key="#Judge">iudex</rs> et <persName
                            key="#Judge" ref="#people/5053">octabianus</persName>
                        <rs key="#Judge">iudex</rs> de <placeName ref="#places/5149">monte sancti
                            iohannis </placeName>et <persName key="#Judge" ref="#people/5055">maius
                            sancsi</persName>
                        <rs key="#Judge">iudex</rs>
                        <placeName key="#Villages/settlements" ref="#places/5182"
                            >verolanus</placeName>. et <persName key="#Judge" ref="#people/5054"
                            >roffreda</persName>
                        <rs key="#Judge">iudex</rs>
                        <placeName ref="#places/5183" key="#Villages/settlements"
                            >alatrinus</placeName>. uno consensu preceperunt quatinus predicti viri.
                        Raul videlicet. et gerardus ravennensis. et gerardus desonnino refutarent ad
                        predictam ecclesiam sancti stephani omnia secundum quod in precepto
                        legebatur. Tandem predictus raul. et gerardus ravennensis. et gerardus
                        desonnino refutaverunt. omnia ut superius dixi secundum quod in preceptum
                        inventum fuit iam nominato monasterio beati stephani. Etsi ipsi vel sui
                        heredes vel eorum summissa persona agere vel molestare temptaverint eundem
                        monasterium vel rectorem eiusdem ecclesie qui modo est vel qui pro aliquo
                        tempore obligaverunt se suosque heredes. vel successores componere in
                        palatio nomine pene <rs key="#Penalty">libras decem denariorum
                            papientium</rs>. et post penam solutam hec refutatio vel trasactio firma
                        permaneat semper. Hactum est hoc precipiente domno iordani capuano principi.
                        in presentia <persName key="#Witness #siblingOf" ref="#people/3015"
                            >ionathae</persName> et <persName key="#Witness #siblingOf"
                            ref="#people/5056">bartholomei</persName>
                        <rs key="#siblingOf">germanorum</rs> eius. et <persName key="#Witness"
                            ref="#people/5058">raulis demolisi</persName>. et <persName
                            key="#Witness" ref="#people/5057">rainaldi ridelli</persName>. et
                            <persName key="#Witness"><name ref="Unfredus de Calo">umfridi
                                decalvi</name></persName>. et <persName key="#Witness"
                            ref="#people/3075">riccardi de aquila</persName>. et <persName
                            key="#Witness"><name ref="Pandulfus de Presenzano">pandulphi
                                depresumzanu</name></persName>. et <persName key="#Witness #Count"
                                ><name ref="Gregorius">gregorii</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Count">comitis</rs>. et <persName key="#Witness #childOf"
                            ref="#people/5059">criscenzi</persName>. et <persName
                            key="#Witness #childOf" ref="#people/5060">gottifrede</persName>
                        <rs key="#childOf">filii</rs>
                        <persName ref="#people/5061">iohannis</persName>. <persName
                            key="#Witness #childOf"><name ref="Stephanus f. Teudi"
                            >stephani</name></persName>. et <persName key="#Witness #childOf"><name
                                ref="Littus f. Teudi">litti</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#childOf">filii</rs>
                        <persName><name ref="Teudus">teudi</name></persName>. et ceterorum plurium
                        quorum nomina superfluum est ponere. + Ego rembaldus iudex interfui et
                        scripsi. </ab>
